    <item>
      <title>中国经济低迷加剧了奢侈品牌的反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/luxury-s-rebound-is-proving-elusive-ahead-of-lvmh-and-richemont-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Burberry Group Plc 和 Hugo Boss AG 等公司未能达到已经控制的预期，并且中国的经济数据削弱了近期反弹的机会后，奢侈品股票投资者正在准备迎接更多坏消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/luxury-s-rebound-is-proving-elusive-ahead-of-lvmh-and-richemont-earnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:42:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国提出打击高额透支费用的规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/us-proposes-new-rule-to-end-high-overdraft-fees-in-crack-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府公布了一项期待已久的法规，该法规可能会将最大银行的透支费收入每年削减多达 35 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/us-proposes-new-rule-to-end-high-overdraft-fees-in-crack-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达沃斯现场直播：米莱赞扬企业英雄，布林肯的飞机失事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/davos-live-global-elite-braces-for-some-argentine-showmanship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷非传统的新总统哈维尔·米莱在世界经济论坛上向合唱团宣讲，称赞商界精英为“英雄”，并告诉他们抵制拥抱社会主义的政客。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/davos-live-global-elite-braces-for-some-argentine-showmanship</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 07:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油与股市一起减少损失，而欧佩克看到强劲的需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-17</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势、石油输出国组织(OPEC)看涨的需求预测以及美国的生产中断，油价收窄跌幅，帮助遏制了更广泛市场的避险基调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-17</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 23:51:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
